# Vendored Bitnami subchart archives.
#
# These are fetched on demand via `helm dependency build` (which reads the
# committed Chart.lock to pin exact versions). We commit Chart.yaml's
# `dependencies:` + Chart.lock, NOT the resolved .tgz archives — keeps the repo
# lean and lets CI / installers re-fetch reproducibly from the locked versions.
#
#   helm dependency build infra/helm/<chart>   # populates charts/ from Chart.lock
*/charts/*.tgz
*/charts/
